                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;when the viewfs function is enabled, the following operation will report errors,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;new Path(UUID.randomUUID().toString())&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, I think that we can add the bashPath, like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&quot;new Path(basePath, UUID.randomUUID().toString())&quot;&lt;/p&gt;

